#19501
The Entrance to The Astral Plane~
As you step from the realm of the prime material plane into the realm of
the astral plane, you feel a strange sensation come over your body, like 
you are being transformed into a different kind of being. This is so you
can survive here. The silvery cord you see connected to you is your only
link to the prime material plane. If it is severed, then you are trapped
here, never to see the realm you are accustomed to again. Pray the raiding
bands of githyankis are nowhere near here, it is said that their swords
can sever that cord. *shiver* The thought of being trapped here doesn't set
so well with you.
